---
title: Thai Chicken & Saucy Red Curry Noodles for Dinner with a Spiced Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Salad for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create
something different for lunch the next day! Enjoy a saucy noodle dish with Thai-spiced chicken, then add the rest
of the chicken to a hearty roast pumpkin salad. Extra delicious!

